title: Just A Matter of Time
itunes:title: Just A Matter of Time
description:
We all have things that we’re believing to overcome. It may not look like anything is changing on the outside, but the moment you prayed, God defeated the source that was fighting against you. Stay in faith. It's only a matter of time until you see the fulfillment of His promise!To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
